= ..eexxiitt!!

(from ruby core)
=== IImmpplleemmeennttaattiioonn  ffrroomm  KKeerrnneell
------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Process.exit!(status=false)

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Exits the process immediately. No exit handlers are run.
_s_t_a_t_u_s is returned to the underlying system as the exit
status.

  Process.exit!(true)


